claim: Mark Strong had a role in Robin Hood.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is known for his role in the television series Our Friends in the North and films such as Oliver Twist  (  2005  )  , Syriana  (  2005  )  , RocknRolla  (  2008  )  , Body of Lies  (  2008  )  , The Young Victoria  (  2009  )  , Sherlock Holmes  (  2009  )  , Robin Hood  (  2010  )  , Kick-Ass  (  2010  )  , Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy  (  2011  )  , Green Lantern  (  2011  )  , Zero Dark Thirty  (  2012  )  , John Carter  (  2012  )  , Mindscape  (  2013  )  , The Imitation Game  (  2014  )  , Kingsman : The Secret Service  (  2014  )  , and Grimsby  (  2016  )  .
